summary:
I am a conscious and passionate person who is driven by the ambition to make a difference. I am interested in corporate sustainability and identity establishment and am currently developing my professionality for sustainable development between society, people, and businesses by studying conscious business at university.
I love getting new ideas and insights from various fields.
